{"tid":975967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡站三成八鋼筋樣本不合格","createTime":"2019-01-10T05:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T07:21:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b027e97905e13eed909678e5fa681de5684a741b","tid":975967,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190110/20587870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F20587870&d=NJS9iWJNrGuYhPFqm1V0FMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=31b462bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F20587870&h=f3ec21ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190110/20587870</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月10日 <br />\n<br />\n紅磡站三成八鋼筋樣本不合格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190110/large/18755445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190110%2Flarge%2F18755445.jpg&h=d403d26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鋼筋及螺絲帽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵鑿開石屎檢測沙中綫紅磡站月台層板，路政署昨公佈多11支鋼筋測試樣本，當中6個樣本不合格，至今累積公佈樣本60個，不合格樣本增至23個，比率為38％。其中一個不合格樣本，鋼筋雖然扭入螺絲帽長度僅33.98毫米，但完全沒有外露扭紋，涉嫌曾被剪短。<br />\n<br />\n新公佈的抽驗樣本均是為檢查鋼筋有否被剪短而進行，11個新增樣本全部集中於東西走廊C1至C3區月台層板近西面連續牆底部，其中6個不合格樣本，鋼筋扭入螺絲帽的長度介乎32.59及36.80毫米，全部低於政府已下調的37毫米標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個樣本疑被剪短<br />\n<br />\n今次是首次抽驗東西走廊C2區月台層板近西面連續牆底部位置，全部3個樣本均不合格，其中一個不合格樣本，鋼筋扭入螺絲帽的長度更只有33.98毫米，同時沒有外露扭紋，較正常鋼筋扭紋應有44毫米為短，有被剪短之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n至於東西走廊C1及C3區月台層板近西面連續牆底部，早前港鐵亦曾抽驗，當時C1區全部樣本合格，惟今次抽驗C1區的7個樣本，則出現3個不合格；連同C3區早前3個不合格樣本，反映只是東西走廊月台層板近西面連續牆底部，由C1至C3區都有不合格的情況。<br />\n<br />\n現時公佈樣本已超逾原定檢測168個樣本的三分一，立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會委員田北辰透露，曾與港鐵商討，將鋼筋扭紋少於40毫米的鋼筋扭出，直接量度長度，以了解有否被剪短，惟港鐵認為只需扭出少於30毫米的鋼筋進行量度即可。<br />\n<br />\n■記者伍雅謙  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\nTruth or Dare劫七仔　更生男籲勿貪玩<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n禁止民族黨運作　剝奪市民選舉權　 港民主排73　跌至西非水平"},{"pid":"27fd9691ac61ff12bfb385a6d7f83078690e0dfe","tid":975967,"uid":45250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:27:06.000Z","msg":"....."},{"pid":"1cde7909fc235fa0fa76de64e3912297d677fbad","tid":975967,"uid":6752,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:29:16.000Z","msg":"驗夠未呀,快d通車啦"},{"pid":"ef86815bf6eee3ac5e5bbc146a82cd25e45a0c0a","tid":975967,"uid":20835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"我話俾你聽ok就ok！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167149e6812b7cc4e05329c50a24ebf421f26aac","tid":975967,"uid":204480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"仲以為全部都唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165fe71ce8a6a54179b8db63e8a099634e8f214b","tid":975967,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"167149e6812b7cc4e05329c50a24ebf421f26aac","tid":975967,"uid":204480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"仲以為全部都唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"已經降左標準都唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059e6d63022eba53025771449a95b4763071dd60","tid":975967,"uid":35667,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"通車啦等住搭呀大佬"},{"pid":"dc958715020e8a30a3ca1b7310532573cc41251a","tid":975967,"uid":102132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b132a8d200af9d03aee260a5f72e7a60a3b603d5","tid":975967,"uid":48134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi